entification.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aElectionszUnited States. 0aPresidentszUnited StatesxElection. 0aVotingzUnited States. 4aAmerican Studies : American Culture. 4aPolitics and Law : Democracy. 4aPolitics and Law : Electoral Politics. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Process / Campaigns & Elections.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978079147817240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791478172423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791478172/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles